Generic single-database configuration for Alembic.

## Usage

### Create a new migration

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Add new table"
```

### Apply migrations

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback migration

```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history

```bash
alembic history
```

### View current version

```bash
alembic current
```
